title: Ayotte, McCain Write to Secretary James on A-10 Readiness Requirements (Kelly Ayotte)
text: ( Source : Kelly Ayotte ) WASHINGTON, D.C. - Today , U.S. Senator Kelly Ayotte (R-NH) and Chairman of the Senate Armed Services Committee ( SASC ), John McCain (R-AZ), as well as eight other senators, sent a letter to Secretary of the Air Force
